aresme","municipi-cerdanya":"","municipi-bergueda":"","municipi-bages":"","municipi-solsones":"","municipi-pirineus":"","disctricte-barcelona":"","tipus-d-article":"Llibre secci\u00f3 Cultura","article-destacat":"1","titol-del-llibre":"El Segrest de l'habitatge : per qu\u00e8 \u00e9s tan dif\u00edcil tenir casa, i com aix\u00f2 pot trencar la societat","autor-a-del-llibre":"Palomera, Jaime","any-edicio":"2025","editorial":"P\u00f2rtic","patrocinat-per":"BIBLIOTECA POPULAR \/ MATAR\u00d3","pagina-del-patrocinador":"https:\/\/biblioteques.culturamataro.cat\/som-les-biblios\/horaris-i-contacte","disposem-de-pdf-de-lectura-previa":false,"pdf-llegir-un-fragment":false,"types_caption":"","types_alt_text":"","types_description":"","types_file_name":"","types_title":""},"55788":{"post_title":"Hamnet","ID":"55788","post_content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>GUANYADORA DEL WOMEN\u2019S PRIZE DE NARRATIVA 2020<\/strong><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>\u201cHipn\u00f2tica i magistral, terriblement \u00edntima. Hauria de guanyar tots els premis literaris de l\u2019any\u201d,\u00a0The Guardian<br>\u201cUna novel\u00b7la espectacular i brillant\u201d, David Mitchell<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>\u2028Un dia d\u2019estiu de l\u2019any 1596, una nena de Stratford-upon-Avon, un poble a prop de Londres, torna de l\u2019escola cansada, amb febre, mal de cap i poques ganes de jugar amb el seu germ\u00e0 bess\u00f3, el Hamnet. Angoixat, ell busca per tota la casa alg\u00fa que pugui ajudar-los, per\u00f2 no hi troba ning\u00fa. La mare, un esperit lliure i exc\u00e8ntric, \u00e9s a m\u00e9s d\u2019un quil\u00f2metre de dist\u00e0ncia, al jard\u00ed on cultiva plantes medicinals, vigilant els ruscos d\u2019abelles. El pare \u00e9s a Londres, treballant al teatre, i la germana gran i l\u2019\u00e0via han anat al poble a comprar. Cap no \u00e9s conscient de la trag\u00e8dia que s\u2019est\u00e0 desfermant a casa seva.\u00a0<br>Hamnet\u00a0\u00e9s la hist\u00f2ria d\u2019una dona fer\u00e9stega i el seu xoriguer, del fill d\u2019un guanter que fuig de la vida que li tocava per casar-se amb la dona que estima i dedicar-se a la seva passi\u00f3, el teatre, i del fill de tots dos, que no passar\u00e0 mai a la hist\u00f2ria per\u00f2 donar\u00e0 t\u00edtol a una de les obres de teatre m\u00e9s c\u00e8lebres de tots els temps. I, al cor de tot plegat, el retrat llumin\u00f3s i viv\u00edssim d\u2019un matrimoni poc convencional, del vincle indestructible entre dos germans bessons i del dolor d\u2019una p\u00e8rdua irreparable, devastadora i trist\u00edssima.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","post_excerpt":"","post_date":"2026-02-16 13:01:37","post_name":"hamnet","post_author":"fabricante","post_status":"publish","featured_image":"https:\/\/www.panxing.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/HAMNET-OFARRELL.jpg","wp_page_template":"","post_format":"standard","comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","pinged":"","post_parent":"0","menu_order":"0","_elementor_template_type":"","_elementor_version":"","_elementor_pro_version":"","_wp_page_template":"","_elementor_edit_mode":"","elementor_library_type":"","_elementor_controls_usage":"","elementor_library_category":"","_elementor_css":"","_elementor_conditions":"","_elementor_page_assets":"a:0:{}","_elementor_page_settings":"","_elementor_data":"","rank_math_focus_keyword":"","rank_math_pillar_content":"","index":"","nofollow":"","noimageindex":"","noindex":"","noarchive":"","nosnippet":"","rank_math_advanced_robots":"","rank_math_canonical_url":"","redirection_type":"","destination_url":"","headline":"","schema_description":"","article_type":"","rank_math_title":"","_wp_old_slug":"","rank_math_description":"","rank_math_facebook_title":"","rank_math_facebook_description":"","rank_math_facebook